(16, 'article 15', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1 style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0em 0px 0.5em; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; padding: 0em; min-height: 1rem; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);">But with the blast shield down, I can\'t even see! How am I supposed to fight?</h1>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif;">I find your lack of faith disturbing. Hey, Luke! May the Force be with you. All right. Well, take care of yourself, Han. I guess that\'s what you\'re best at, ain\'t it? I care. So, what do you think of her, Han?</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; line-height: 1.5; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Don\'t act so surprised, Your Highness. You weren\'t on any mercy mission this time. Several transmissions were beamed to this ship by Rebel spies.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: inherit;">I want to know what happened to the plans they sent you.</strong>&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: inherit;">I care.</em>&nbsp;So, what do you think of her, Han?</p>\r\n<h2 style="box-sizing: inherit; font-family: \'Roboto Slab\', \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);">The Force is strong with this one. I have you now.</h2>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; line-height: 1.5; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">No! Alderaan is peaceful. We have no weapons. You can\'t possibly&hellip; As you wish. All right. Well, take care of yourself, Han. I guess that\'s what you\'re best at, ain\'t it? You don\'t believe in the Force, do you?</p>\r\n<ol style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"